Happy Friday and welcome back to our 89th Weekly Dose of Optimism.
After a weird week of weather events (earthquakes and eclipses), things are=
 starting to normalize again. Normalization is a good thing, because around=
 here a normal week usually means that at least five big, future-shaping th=
ings have happened. This week was no exception.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
